<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{appName}} - {{title}}</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.9.0/styles/atom-one-dark.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.9.0/highlight.min.js"></script>
    <script>hljs.highlightAll();</script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 font-sans antialiased">
    <nav class="bg-indigo-600 text-white shadow-lg fixed w-full z-10 top-0 h-16 flex items-center px-6">
        <div class="text-xl font-bold">{{appName}} <span class="text-indigo-200 text-sm font-normal">Developer Guide</span></div>
    </nav>

    <div class="flex max-w-8xl mx-auto pt-16">
        <aside class="w-64 fixed h-full overflow-y-auto bg-white border-r border-gray-200 p-6 hidden md:block pb-24">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider mb-4">Table of Contents</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li><a href="index.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 {{#if (eq activePage 'index')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}} block">Home & Quick Start</a></li>
                <li class="pt-2 pb-1"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">1. Core Concepts</span></li>
                <li><a href="gdl.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'gdl')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">GDL & Framework</a></li>
                <li><a href="cli.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'cli')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">CLI & Code Injection</a></li>
                <li class="pt-2 pb-1"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">2. APIs</span></li>
                <li><a href="rest.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'rest')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">REST & Generic Search</a></li>
                <li><a href="graphql.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'graphql')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">GraphQL Integration</a></li>
                <li><a href="grpc.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'grpc')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">Secured gRPC (Kratos)</a></li>
                <li class="pt-2 pb-1"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">3. Real-Time & Audit</span></li>
                <li><a href="realtime.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'realtime')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">WebSockets & MQTT</a></li>
                <li><a href="audit.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'audit')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">Audit & Metering</a></li>
                <li class="pt-2 pb-1"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">4. Infrastructure</span></li>
                <li><a href="security.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'security')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">Security & Resilience</a></li>
                <li><a href="observability.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'observability')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">Observability</a></li>
                <li class="pt-2 pb-1"><span class="font-semibold text-gray-800">5. Examples</span></li>
                <li><a href="integrations.html" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 pl-4 block {{#if (eq activePage 'integrations')}}font-bold text-indigo-600{{/if}}">Client Integrations</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>

        <main class="flex-1 md:ml-64 p-8 lg:p-12 max-w-5xl">
            {{{body}}}
            <footer class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 text-center text-gray-500 text-sm pb-12">
                Generated with ❤️ by GO-DUCK CLI
            </footer>
        </main>
